      "content": "idk i just feel like i'm being told to do something that doesn't make sense. if i'm not sick anymore, why would i need more medicine? i've read online that taking antibiotics when you don't need them can actually mess up your gut microbiome and cause more problems down the road. wouldn't it be more \"scientific\" to just stop once the infection is cleared? can't you just tell me if it's safe to stop? i dont want to wait days for a doctor to call me back.",
